name: Christmas Snow Pixie
description: A Christmas moment from Miss Suomi, though nobody is entirely sure what happened. "I bet you anything her skirt got flipped," said AK47, "Though I don't know what's so embarrassing about it. It's just us, plus an extra commander." "That's what you'd call A+ acting," snickered Makarov.

name: Kvass Tank
description: Authentic kvass. Only those who will drink it to their heart's content deserve its delicious taste.

name: The Feast on Christmas Eve
description: A precious photo taken before the feast on Christmas Eve. Precious because both the T-Dolls and the food were in ghastly state after the feast had started.

name: Christmas Eve Lodge
description: Although they say Christmas and presents are inseparable...you should still leave some room to walk through.

name: Zombie Homebody
description: A photo of Miss Halloween Gr G11 taken during a certain moment. According to M99's recountal, "I don't know what happened. Gr G11 was already like this when I came to." As for what happened to Gr G11 before M99 regained consciousness may be the biggest mystery of this Halloween.

name: Kitty Party
description: A photo of Miss Halloween Vector taken during a certain moment. "No one besides the Commander has seen this photo. Of course, there could've been others that were spirited away, so I'm the first tooo~..." The note next to the photo was interrupted here. The last bit of unfinished handwriting is evidence of what may be the scariest tragedy tonight.

name: Spooky Kitty
description: A kitty of unknown origins, or perhaps someone dressed it up to the point of being an unrecognizable little monster. It likes to jump onto people as if it is in search of something... It's probably better to not investigate too deeply into this.

name: Halloween Fright
description: A precious photograph taken at a party on a Halloween night. After the lively party was over, Gr G11 who was totally asleep was left there for the night.

name: Demon Hunter
description: A photo of Thompson taken during battle. Even a hunter like her can make a mistake sometimes, but it is only because of her scars that she is this elegant and reliable.

name: Black Sports Motorcycle
description: AEK999's beloved vehicle. Because she changes her attire before going out for a ride, only her close riding buddies know of the existence of this vehicle.

name: Theatre Performance
description: A photograph of the theatre before the start of the performance. Everything is under control, except for what the Commander has wreaked upon his arrival.

name: The Smile of the Goddess of Red Packets
description: Those who received a red packet were very happy, and Miss Gd DSR-50 also received a new nickname.

name: Spring Festival Bar
description: The elaborately decorated banquet hall by M590 on Chinese New Year's Eve features an Oriental-style bar.

name: Epitome of Femininity
description: Blooming only after the rest withers, it is revered as the empress of flowers. Praised for its unparalleled splendor, it is the first to bestow the worldly realm with its fragrant savor.

name: Melancholic Bride
description: A picture of an expression that does not seem to match her attire. It is exactly this sense of dissonance that makes this photo worth saving.

name: Elite N.E.E.T. Sign
description: Another sign that reveals the true purpose of life. But is this "truth" reality?

name: Wedding Curtains
description: The bouquets on the curtains remind you of that sweet moment, even if it is filled with happiness that is not your own.

name: Cathedral
description: You can't help but be serious when you enter this solemn building. The promises made here may be the sincerest of them all.

name: Icon: Anniversary Special Kalina
description: The year together with the Commander was really fun! Please continue to spend just as much next year~

name: Furniture: Steel Giant
description: A painting that looks as if it's world famous. It gives you a heavy feeling in your heart every time you look at it…

name: ID Card: Our Year Together
description: Remember, this edited photo must never be shown to certain important people that were cut out from the left side of the image.

name: Gems Agent
description: Experienced agents will always don an identity before their mission. An exquisitely crafted calling card is also a symbol of professionalism.

name: Time Throne
description: There is no such thing as an eternal throne. Power is like fine sand; it will leak from your grasp bit by bit.

name: Icon: The Perfect Exchange
description: Both the buyer and the seller will show a contented smile after the fulfillment of their wishes.

name: Icon: Aristocrat's Taste Test
description: ...Well, I finally made a half decent cup of tea. How does it taste, Commander?

name: ID Card: Maid Internship
description:
Although they can't provide as perfect of an experience as a real maid cafe...
being able to see this side of them here is still worth the price.

name: Background: Cozy Cafe
description: Regardless if you're a human or a T-Doll, feel free to drop by and relax whenever you're worn out.

name: ID: Beach Party
description: The T-Dolls at Griffin are unexpectedly given a short and peaceful summer vacation, but the beach might be more than what it seems... Will the T-Dolls really be able to enjoy this "peaceful" vacation?

name: Icon: Beach Punk 2064
description: Gr G41! Here we go! Please watch my performance, Master!

name: Furniture: Fel in Diving Suit
description: To commemorate the adventures on the beach, Fel got a new outfit... Not sure when it's gonna come in useful, but FAL's happy about it, and that's what matters!

name: Icon: Pumpkin Skewers
description: S.A.T.8, a T-Doll who constantly slides back and forth between being unperturbed and being dead serious, what could possibly have pushed her to the far end on the other side of her neural cloud's scales this time?

name: Furniture: Ghost Trap, Counterattack!
description: Is this the biggest pinch that the Invincible No. 1 Netizen MDR has ever faced? Who could have done something so...amusing? (MDR: delete plz)

name: Furniture: Witch's Forest Wallpaper
description: This picture was taken during a private Griffin Halloween party. That night...all the Dolls in the picture...changed back to their regular clothes.

name: ID: Guns N' Side Boxes
description: Is this merely a festive costume, or is it the real monster that I am? I'm like the side boxes on your motorcycle. You don't see me, but I'm always looking at you...as you travel to your next destination...

name: Furniture: Bionic Pig Charger
description: This bionic pig-shaped mobile charger can quickly charge T-Dolls and has many adaptors to handle various circumstances... "Adaptors? What do you mean by adaptors?" Gr MP5 asks.

name: Furniture: Door Guardian Window Cutouts
description: A paper cutout that Type95 made after witnessing the events of Chinese New Year Eve. "I won't have two dummies who froze themselves solid on Chinese New Year's Eve as my door guardians! Send them back to where they came from!" Type97 said after seeing it.

name: Icon: Sangria Succulent
description: "Happy New Year. I hope you will keep it up in the coming year. I'll look forward to your performance."

name: ID: Sangria Succulent
description: "Even though it's a joy to share good wine with others, drinking alone from time to time can also be a luxury."

name: Furniture: Magic Dressing Table
description: Sufficiently advanced science is indistinguishable from magic. No Doll can resist the magic that makes them beautiful, and so they sit here for long periods of time.

name: Icon: The Most Beautiful Smile
description: The best shot is taken when the owner of the smile feels genuinely happy.

name: Furniture: Sweet Selection
description: There is no luck in life, only individual choices. Of course, there are times when you don't want to choose... Then again, choosing everything is also a choice.

name: ID: Blissful Mission
description: She is the emissary of happiness and hope. Only the person who gives her a mission can see what she really looks like.

name: Furniture: Tactical Stealth Box
description: The contemporary Romeo won't have to climb up a balcony to see Juliet. All he needs to do is put Juliet in this stealth box, and she can elope with him as safely and comfortably as if she were sitting on a train.

name: Furniture: Operation Ball Girl
description: The girls look absolutely stunning on the stage. If there is always such a performance in every random gala, I'd look forward to it even if it is a total farce.

name: Icon: "Seizing First Place"
description: "T-The bet is on! Even if I come in last, I'll gladly take the punishment!"

name: Furniture: Custom Orange Kitty Lifeguard
description: A new model of orange lifeguard kitty equipped with cutting-edge gear reports for duty! But who can this frail little kitty save in the vast ocean? It can't even save itself.

name: Icon: Summer Memories
description: Though that girl's luck didn't follow her into these waters...being able to capture her leisurely smile might be a sign that her luck went to me instead.

name: Furniture: Mermaid Stand
description: To soothe the disappointment of not seeing any mermaids, the Commander had this mermaid stand especially created for the T-Dolls. But T-Dolls with a big head should refrain from squeezing in too hard...

name: ID: R-Type Over-The-Shoulder Throw
description: Eh?! Aw, since we're at the beach, let's not play cards! How about an exciting sports competition? As for the events...hehe, how about THIS?

name: Furniture: "Shall we play a game?"
description: "...Sis? Don't be afraid. There's so much I can do. I can protect you. I can even... Heheh, shall we play a game?"

name: Furniture: Space Gentledog
description: "I. Super star dancer. Gold farming." "Kalina?! The dog translator you just bought really does work! ...Wait, no! Come and see what kind of scary stuff this dog translator just said!"

name: Icon: "No treat, but don't trick"
description: "(Sob) I've been working so hard for these grocery store coupons... You've already tricked me, so why are you scaring me as well?!"

name: ID Card: Feast of the Monstrous
description: "Night falls. This is when the monstrous creeps out from the shadows within the Griffin compound..." "No, cut! Again! If you don't do this properly, I won't give you your soda or your discount coupons!"

name: Furniture: X'mas Sock Full of Presents
description: A modest-looking X'mas Sock that contains the well wishes and kindness of countless people - "Which makes this a perfectly safe place to hide," thinks a certain dinergate infiltrating Griffin. Hopefully it will deliver the presents successfully.

name: Furniture: Vixen User Manual
description: A manual for "Vixen", a mech built especially for Christmas... Even though it can't soar through the sky, it can still deliver your presents! It's really hardworking!

name: Icon: Smile of the Mistletoe
description: The beautiful legend about the girl who's pure as snow guarding the mistletoe - in the merciless cold of winter, other than a hot bowl of soup, the girl's smile can also warm you right up.

name: ID: Florentine's X'mas Tree
description: The joy of Christmas isn't about any person, it's about the Christmas tree that was planted to make everyone smile happily... That's the most charming thing about Christmas Night!

name: Furniture: Sticker of Good Fortune
description: A sticker that bears the Dolls' well-wishing. Someone stuck it on the Commander's door.

name: Furniture: Space Chair
description: This is a miraculous chair. Just sit on it, relax, close your eyes and count to five, then everything will change...

name: Icon: Whispers in the Candlelight
description: Outside the window is the ceaseless and boisterous sound of exploding firecrackers; inside the house is a sleepless New Year's night. Why not light a candle and have a late-night heart-to-heart with someone you care about?

name: ID: New Year Rituals
description: Is there a better New Year gift than waking up from a short nap and finding oneself surrounded by gifts? Right now, the Commander is inclined to answer in the negative.

name: Furniture: Secret Recorder
description: Things that document the truth are never immediately visible. Guess how many camera heads there are in here?

name: Icon: Invaluable True Feelings
description: She is willing to always give you the benefit of the doubt when things happen – this is how she interprets the concept of "trust".

name: ID: Perfect Ending
description: Everything comes to a peaceful resolution on this day. Have you thought about how to respond to all the genuine feelings they have shown you?

name: ID: Witness of the Starry Night
description: As the meteor falls, a pair of eyes are taking in the starry sky – her eyes are much better than RMB-93's camera.

name: Furniture: "Standstill"
description: Though Death has brought me to a halt, please remember me by this... I have lived.

name: Furniture: "Concept"
description: Please, please, please specify if it's a banquet or a party next time you promote an event. There's a huge difference in scale between the two.

name: Icon: "Goal"
description: Do not hesitate, do not be distracted. Try to think – what exactly is your goal?

name: ID: "Debate"
description: Impossible! My way is definitely better! I'm calling for a vote on the forum! —Zas M76
